commentText: Wraps the given Hadoop S3 File System object as a Flink S3 File System object._The given Hadoop file system object is expected to be initialized already.__@param hadoopS3FileSystem The Hadoop FileSystem that will be used under the hood.

Creates a FlinkS3FileSystem based on the given Hadoop S3 file system._The given Hadoop file system object is expected to be initialized already.__@param hadoopS3FileSystem The Hadoop FileSystem that will be used under the hood.
